rComments: Great Professor, very knowledgable and clear. He seems to be tough, but actually he is trying to help his students to learn and become a professional engineer. He is also a nice person. His grade is fair and his exam is close to the materials in class. Also, his english speed and words picked are good for international students.
He can be sooo rude!  Very arrogant.
A wonderful professor (was also my advisor).  Was hard, expected a lot from his students, but I know I benefitted from it, and wish I had many more professors like him.
